1
00:00:01,467 --> 00:00:03,900
This app doesn't ask what you want to do.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:05,633
It asks who you want to become.

3
00:00:05,733 --> 00:00:10,733
Tell an AI coach your goal, and it builds a real plan.

4
00:00:11,267 --> 00:00:14,833
Milestones and small daily actions.

5
00:00:14,933 --> 00:00:16,733
Check off your day —

6
00:00:16,833 --> 00:00:19,033
and it says so.

7
00:00:19,133 --> 00:00:20,467
Each week, your coach checks in.

8
00:00:20,567 --> 00:00:23,100
Tell it what's hard,

9
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:28,200
and it adapts the plan to how you're doing.

10
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:31,400
Resolution Companion — free on the App Store.
